are encouraged to call or email devon direct any time for an update on an outstanding issue inquiry reason please selectupdate account informationdirect depositoildex login informationproblemrevenue paymentjoint interest billing paymentstatementtransfer an ownership in a wellreport a death of an ownerquestions about a division order receivedinvoice payment status  ap vendortaxunclaimed propertyother name i am an please selectownersupplierother email phone number business associate or vendor number message a qualified analyst will get you the information you need hours of operation  am to  pm cst monday through thursday and  am to  pm cst on friday canadian operations for royalty owner inquiries relating to canadian operations and wells please email royaltyadministrationdvncom devon canada ap inquiries apdvncom questions for investors questions for job seekers frequently asked questions interest owners suppliers useful resources and links oildex owner account access jiblink american petroleum institute american royalty council apis energy tomorrow owner resource guide royalty owners  producers educational coalition download forms direct deposit for owners owner change of address social responsibility disclaimer you are now leaving devon energy’s website and are going to a website that is not operated by devon energy we are not responsible for the content or availability of linked sites about third party links on our site devon energy offers links to other third party websites that may be of interest to our website visitors when you click on these links you will leave devon energy’s website and will be redirected to another site these sites are not under the control of devon energydevon energy is not responsible for the content of linked third party websites we are not an agent for these third parties nor do we endorse or guarantee any of their opinions ideas products or content  we make no representation or warranty regarding the accuracy of the information contained